description: Marriage is difficult! It is even more difficult when you haven't discussed some of the most basic marriage topics. How many children do we want to have? How would we handle being broke? This skill is a fun way to get you and your partner talking about some of these topics. Simply ask Alexa for a wedding topic, discuss with your partner, then ask for another.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask wedding topics for a marriage topic
Alexa, ask wedding topics to suggest a topic
Alexa, ask wedding topics to ask us a question
name: Before the Knot
shortDescription: Are you ready for marriage? This skill will help you find out by suggesting conversation topics you will want to discuss before taking the big step.
